					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610225788" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;" >Taffeta</a></span> <span class="odate time_1448081129 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">21 Nov 2015 04:45</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2411212">
									

<p>&quot;Sir, how many members of the O5 council are there?&quot; one rookie asked, from the back of the auditorium.<br />
The Senior Agent blinked, before replying, &quot;Twelve.&quot;<br />
Murmurs of dissent rippled around the auditorium as the new staff looked at each other in consternation. Wasn't this guy meant to know this off by heart? Hadn't he had over ten years' worth of experience under these very people?<br />
Another dissident stood up from his seat. &quot;Doesn't the booklet say that there are 13 council members?&quot;<br />
&quot;No, it's just that we have an O5-13, that's all. I'll count 'em all for you. O5-1, O5-2, O5-3, O5-4, O5-6, O5-7, all the way to O5-13.&quot;<br />
&quot;But, sir, what about the fifth one?&quot;<br />
The Agent stared back at him blankly. &quot;O5&#8230;5?&quot;<br />
&quot;Yeah, that one.&quot;<br />
&quot;What do you mean, that one? We've never <em>had</em> an O5-5.&quot;</p>

							</div>

								
					
