			<div class="content" id="post-content-1280953">
									

<p>The way I interpreted this was that this anomalous affect kept showing up <em>not</em> in the Foundation universe, just in a world like ours- and maybe later people can explore some and find all the documentation it it for these things that don't exist. From there, I thought about the documentation, and then how we (the meta-authors) would also be wrapped up in that, only this clearly isn't <em>our</em> world, so&#8230;<br />
Well, it's an imaginative article, and I'm not sure how much of my extrapolation was intended, but you get a plus-one for making this reader experience some unexpected existential panic.</p>

